      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent analyst review of model setup; documented checklist covering boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions.",
      "rationale": "A second analyst independently reviewed model setup files against a 24-item checklist. Boundary condition application (fixed inferior block, displacement-controlled superior block per F1717 fixture geometry) and Ti-6Al-4V material properties confirmed correct. No use errors identified."
