      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from ASTM-certified coupon tests on same material lot; geometric inputs from CMM measurements of test articles.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (2.2 GPa) derived from tensile coupon testing per ASTM E8. Screw and rod geometry inputs obtained from CMM measurements of the 11 test constructs with tolerances propagated through sensitivity analysis. Input uncertainty quantified and incorporated into validation metric."
