      "rationale": "The validation activity directly replicates the COU: same device design, same test standard (ASTM F1717), same loading mode (static compression-bending), same QoIs. No spatial, temporal, or loading-regime extrapolation is required. The validation evidence is therefore directly applicable to the regulatory submission decision."
